{
  "texts": [
    "Managers should prioritize the implementation of strategies that cultivate enthusiasm, commitment, and absorption among their workforce.",
    "The study suggests that organizations should establish a work environment that is supportive and positive, fostering employee engagement.",
    "This can be accomplished by providing opportunities for professional growth, promoting a healthy work-life balance, and acknowledging and rewarding employee contributions.",
    "In essence, the study presents actionable implications for managers and leaders in public universities, underlining the significance of employee engagement in driving organizational performance.",
    "By adopting approaches to fortify employee engagement, organizations can enhance productivity, retention rates, and overall success."
  ]
}